## ðŸ“‹ Quick Reference

### ðŸŽ¯ Core Formulas
```
Build:     P[j] = P[j-1] + A[j]
Query:     SUM(i,j) = P[j] - P[i-1]  (if i > 0)
           SUM(0,j) = P[j]           (if i == 0)
```

### ðŸ“Š Complexity Summary
```
Build: O(n) time, O(n) space
Query: O(1) time
```

### ðŸŽ¯ Use Cases
- Static array with many range sum queries
- Subarray problems
- 2D matrix problems
- Foundation for advanced data structures

